<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
		<title>EMA625_05_IH_0003</title>

		<!-- 공통 js-->
		<script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
		<script src="../../common_practice/common/js/solve_area_act.js"></script>

		<!-- 공통 css-->
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

		<!-- 개별 -->
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/common/css/app.css" />
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/css/ema625_05.css" />
	</head>

	<body>
		<div id="app_wrap" class="ema624_05_ih_0003 paging">
			<section class="title type2 score">
				<h2 data-head="3_light_purple" lang="y">
					정육각형을 이용하여 원의 넓이를 어림하려고 합니다. 물음에 답해 보세요.
				</h2>
			</section>

			<section class="contents paging_layout">
				<article class="page page_1">
					<h3 class="title" lang="y">
						삼각형 ㄱㅇㄴ의 넓이가 15 ㎠일 때, 원 안에 있는 초록색 정육각형의 넓이는 몇 ㎠인지 구해 보세요.
					</h3>

					<div class="question_box justify_center align_center">
						<div class="img_area">
							<img src="./../../common_practice/img/EMA625_05_IH/0003_01.png" alt="" />
							<p class="text1">ㄱ</p>
							<p class="text2">ㄴ</p>
							<p class="text3">ㄷ</p>
							<p class="text4">ㄹ</p>
							<p class="text5">ㅇ</p>
						</div>
						<div class="flex align_center">
							<div class="input_wrap">
								<math-field data-answer-single="90"></math-field>
							</div>
							<span lang="y">㎠</span>
						</div>
					</div>
					<!-- 해설 -->
					<div class="solve_area">
						<div class="inner_solve">
							<div class="flex">
								<strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
								<div class="conts_solve">
									<p lang="y">
										(원 안에 있는 초록색 정육각형의 넓이)=(삼각형 ㄱㅇㄴ의 넓이)×6<br />=15×6=90
										(㎠)
									</p>
								</div>
							</div>
							<div class="buttons_solve"></div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</article>

				<article class="page page_2">
					<h3 class="title" lang="y">
						삼각형 ㄷㅇㄹ의 넓이가 20 ㎠일 때, 원 밖에 있는 빨간색 정육각형의 넓이는 몇 ㎠인지 구해 보세요.
					</h3>

					<div class="question_box justify_center align_center">
						<div class="img_area">
							<img src="./../../common_practice/img/EMA625_05_IH/0003_01.png" alt="" />
							<p class="text1">ㄱ</p>
							<p class="text2">ㄴ</p>
							<p class="text3">ㄷ</p>
							<p class="text4">ㄹ</p>
							<p class="text5">ㅇ</p>
						</div>
						<div class="flex align_center">
							<div class="input_wrap">
								<math-field data-answer-single="120"></math-field>
							</div>
							<span lang="y">㎠</span>
						</div>
					</div>
					<!-- 해설 -->
					<div class="solve_area">
						<div class="inner_solve">
							<div class="flex">
								<strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
								<div class="conts_solve">
									<p lang="y">
										(원 밖에 있는 빨간색 정육각형의 넓이)=(삼각형 ㄷㅇㄹ의 넓이)×6<br />=20×6=120
										(㎠)
									</p>
								</div>
							</div>
							<div class="buttons_solve"></div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</article>
				<article class="page page_3">
					<h3 class="title" lang="y">원의 넓이를 어림해 보세요.</h3>

					<div class="question_box justify_center align_center">
						<div class="img_area">
							<img src="./../../common_practice/img/EMA625_05_IH/0003_01.png" alt="" />
							<p class="text1">ㄱ</p>
							<p class="text2">ㄴ</p>
							<p class="text3">ㄷ</p>
							<p class="text4">ㄹ</p>
							<p class="text5">ㅇ</p>
						</div>
						<div class="input_area">
							<img src="./../../common_practice/img/EMA625_05_IH/0003_02.png" alt="" />
							<div>
								<div class="flex align_center input_row">
									<span lang="y">원의 넓이는</span>
									<div class="input_wrap ml_10">
										<math-field data-answer-single="90"></math-field>
									</div>
									<span lang="y">㎠보다 넓고</span>
								</div>
								<div class="flex align_center input_row">
									<div class="input_wrap">
										<math-field data-answer-single="120"></math-field>
									</div>
									<span lang="y">㎠보다 좁습니다.</span>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
					<!-- 해설 -->
					<div class="solve_area">
						<div class="inner_solve">
							<div class="flex">
								<strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
								<div class="conts_solve">
									<p lang="y">원의 넓이는 90 ㎠보다 넓고 120 ㎠보다 좁습니다</p>
								</div>
							</div>
							<div class="buttons_solve"></div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</article>

				<div class="btn_area">
					<button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
					<button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
					<button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
				</div>
			</section>
		</div>
	</body>
</html>
